Package: openstuffit
Architecture: any
Depends:
 ${misc:Depends},
 ${shlibs:Depends}
Description: CLI tool for inspecting and extracting StuffIt archives
 openstuffit is a command line tool for identify/list/dump/extract/create
 operations on classic StuffIt archives and wrappers.

Package: libopenstuffit0
Section: libs
Architecture: any
Multi-Arch: same
Depends:
 ${misc:Depends},
 ${shlibs:Depends}
Description: runtime shared library for openstuffit
 libopenstuffit0 provides the runtime shared library used by openstuffit and
 applications linking against the openstuffit C API.

Package: libopenstuffit-dev
Section: libdevel
Architecture: any
Multi-Arch: same
Depends:
 ${misc:Depends},
 libopenstuffit0 (= ${binary:Version})
Description: development files for openstuffit
 libopenstuffit-dev provides headers, pkg-config metadata, and development
 linker files for the openstuffit C API.
